paragraphs.title: Create column distribution table and register it like temp view

msg.data:
defined class HistRow
createHistogramTableAndRegister: (df: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame, columnName: String, viewName: String)Unit

paragraphs.text:
val inputMatrix = df.rdd.map{r=> 
  val array = r.toSeq.toArray 
  val values = array.map(_ match { case i: Int => i case f: Float => f case d: Double => d }) 
  org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.Vectors.dense(values)
}
  
val corrMatrix = Statistics.corr(inputMatrix, "pearson")
val cols = (0 until corrMatrix.numCols).toSeq
val df_corr_arr =corrMatrix.transpose
  .colIter.toSeq
  .map(_.toArray)
  .toDF("arr")

val df_corr = cols.foldLeft(df_corr_arr)((df_corr_arr, i) => df_corr_arr.withColumn("_" + (i+1), $"arr"(i)))
  .drop("arr")
  
 df_corr.createOrReplaceTempView("corr")
